        //   c  = ΣW − ΣW²/ΣW = 2   (DL denominator)
        // ================================================================
        // ----------------------------------------------------------------
        // HS — Hunter-Schmidt
        // τ²_HS = max(0, (Q−df) / ΣW) = (4.667−2)/3 = 8/9 ≈ 0.889
        // ----------------------------------------------------------------
